## Introduction
Hello, I'm Kaushal Patel, an energetic and passionate Engineering student at Shah and Anchor Kutchhi Engineering College. As a tech-enthusiast, I am naturally curious and eager to learn new technologies, always excited to apply my knowledge and gain insights from experienced professionals in real-world settings. My ability to effectively self-manage during independent projects, as well as collaborate productively in teams, has been demonstrated through my active involvement with IEEE SAKEC and IIC SAKEC. I have designed visually engaging graphics for event branding, led a team of organizers for various events, and headed the graphics team for the SAKEC Maratho. Additionally, I have participated in hackathons and volunteered for college fests and IEEE Bombay Section events, continuously honing my skills and contributing to the community.
